data.description: Pride of ownership throughout. Flow through this nice, open, two story, 4 bedroom, 3 bath, with a 3 car garage!! Cozy up by the living room fire place, or rest inside the spacious master suite and bath. Serve breakfast on Corian counter tops or breakfast nook, after breakfast walk through the patio door and enjoy the sunny outdoors with a large back yard and desert landscaping. Close to schools, water park and community center with pool!!
